Subject: [PATCH] backport uvm warning fixes from 535.146.02

---
 nvidia-uvm/uvm_va_block.c | 2 +-
 nvidia-uvm/uvm_va_block.h | 2 +-
 2 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/nvidia-uvm/uvm_va_block.c b/nvidia-uvm/uvm_va_block.c
index 88fdefca..08695891 100644
--- a/nvidia-uvm/uvm_va_block.c
